description: young woman with wavy blonde bobbed hair wearing a strapless smocked plaid dress in front of a French fry booth; arm of person with UPC code wrist tattoo at right
text: Minnesota photographer Michael Dvorak places empathy at the core of his camera practice. Through searching photographic portraits, Dvorak reflects the diversity of Minnesota’s many communities as well as the humanity of each individual sitter.
title: Pine City, MN [young woman wearing smocked plaid dress in front of French fry booth]
